# Code of Conduct

- Our Pledge
We are committed to providing a welcoming and inclusive environment for everyone.

- Our Standards
Examples of positive behavior include respect, collaboration, and empathy.

- Enforcement Responsibilities
Project maintainers are responsible for enforcing this Code of Conduct.

- Scope
This Code of Conduct applies to all project spaces and interactions.

- Enforcement
Inappropriate behavior will result in corrective actions such as warnings or removal from the project.

- Enforcement Guidelines
Actions may include warnings, temporary bans, or permanent removal from the project.

- Attribution
This Code of Conduct is adapted from community best practices.
